                    <h2>HTML5 / CSS3</h2>
                    <p>So you've heard of HTML5 and CSS3, maybe you know what it is and maybe you do not. Either way every page I build has the latest techonology.</p><p> But what does it mean for a business? It means you get a site that works everywhere and looks great. Search engines like google.com love HTML5 because it makes your content more relevant. Customers love CSS3 because it makes your site beautiful. You will love them both for those same reasons and the fact that it's quicker to develop which means it's cheaper too.</p>
                    <p><a class="btn" href="#">Learn More &raquo;</a></p>
